modules.description: This module enables styling text with foreground/background colors and attributes (like bold or underline) and manipulating terminal output through cursor positioning, screen clearing, and dynamic resizing in ANSI-compliant environments. It provides types for color and style definitions, along with functions to save/restore cursor states, query terminal dimensions, and perform inline updates. These capabilities are particularly useful for building interactive command-line interfaces, visual progress indicators, and text-based user interactions that require precise terminal control.
